e());\n        }\n    }\n\n    static final class TestDelegatingInstantiator<T> extends DelegatingToExoticInstantiator<T> {\n        TestDelegatingInstantiator(Class<T> type) {\n            super(SampleExoticInstantiator.class.getName(), type);\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780855917535}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_YWXkurpkIo5Adb4gzONpe7Aw|fc_0bbd0702d374584f016a25b46d47d08194bbb1d390bfb72ed2", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\nplugins {\n    id \"org.graalvm.internal.tck\"\n}\n\nString libraryVersion = tck.testedLibraryVersion.get()\n\ndependencies {\n    testImplementation \"org.springframework:spring-core:$libraryVersion\"\n    testImplementation 'org.jboss:jboss-vfs:3.2.15.Final'\n    testImplementation 'org.eclipse.platform:org.eclipse.equinox.common:3.14.0'\n    testImplementation 'org.osgi:org.osgi.core:6.0.0'\n    testImplementation 'org.assertj:assertj-core:3.22.0'\n}\n\nTaskProvider<Test> openedDefineClassTest = tasks.register('openedDefineClassTest', Test) {\n    description = 'Exercises the ClassLoader.defineClass path that needs java.lang opened.'\n    group = 'verification'\n    testClassesDirs = sourceSets.test.output.classesDirs\n    classpath = sourceSets.test.runtimeClasspath\n    useJUnitPlatform()\n    jvmArgs '--add-opens=java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED'\n    filter {\n        includeTestsMatching 'org_springframework.spring_core.ReflectUtilsTest.' +\n                'defineClassUsesProtectedClassLoaderDefineClassWithoutContextClass'\n    }\n}\n\ntasks.named('test') {\n    filter {\n        excludeTestsMatching 'org_springframework.spring_core.ReflectUtilsTest.' +\n                'defineClassUsesProtectedClassLoaderDefineClassWithoutContextClass'\n    }\n    dependsOn openedDefineClassTest\n}\n\ngraalvmNative {\n    agent {\n        defaultMode = \"conditional\"\n        modes {\n            conditional {\n                userCodeFilterPath = \"user-code-filter.json\"\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    binaries {\n        all {\n            buildArgs.add('--add-opens=java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED')\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780855917535}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_d9oMCLnSmTOIvME2nEbpPQuw|fc_0bbd0702d374584f016a25b46d47d8819483720e4d58af4859", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage org_springframework.spring_core;\n\nimport java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicInteger;\n\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n\nimport org.springframework.objenesis.SpringObjenesis;\n\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\n\npublic class SunReflectionFactoryHelperTest {\n\n    @Test\n    void springObjenesisCreatesInstancesWithoutCallingTargetConstructor() {\n        ConstructorBypassedComponent.constructorCalls.set(0);\n        final SpringObjenesis objenesis = new SpringObjenesis();\n\n        final ConstructorBypassedComponent instance = objenesis.newInstance(ConstructorBypassedComponent.class);\n\n        assertThat(instance).isNotNull();\n        assertThat(ConstructorBypassedComponent.constructorCalls).hasValue(0);\n        assertThat(instance.message).isNull();\n        assertThat(instance.number).isZero();\n    }\n\n    private static final class ConstructorBypassedComponent {\n\n        private static final AtomicInteger constructorCalls = new AtomicInteger();\n\n        private final String message;\n\n        private final int number;\n\n        private ConstructorBypassedComponent() {\n            constructorCalls.incrementAndGet();\n            this.message = \"constructed\";\n            this.number = 42;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780855917535}]}
